<p><span id="RM"></span><span style="font-weight: bold">Requested moves</span>
</p>
<ul><li>06 Jun 2020 &#8211; <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Misinformation_related_to_the_COVID-19_pandemic" title="Misinformation related to the COVID-19 pandemic">Misinformation related to the COVID-19 pandemic</a> <span class="plainlinks"><small>(<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Talk:Misinformation_related_to_the_COVID-19_pandemic" title="Talk:Misinformation related to the COVID-19 pandemic">talk</a>&#160;·&#160;<a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Misinformation_related_to_the_COVID-19_pandemic&amp;action=edit">edit</a>&#160;·&#160;<a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Misinformation_related_to_the_COVID-19_pandemic&amp;action=history">hist</a>)</small></span> is requested to be moved to <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Misinformation_related_to_the_COVID-19&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Misinformation related to the COVID-19 (page does not exist)">Misinformation related to the COVID-19</a> by <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User:Soumya-8974" title="User:Soumya-8974">Soumya-8974</a> <small>(<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User_talk:Soumya-8974" title="User talk:Soumya-8974">t</a>&#160;·&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:Contributions/Soumya-8974" title="Special:Contributions/Soumya-8974">c</a>)</small>; see <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Talk:Misinformation_related_to_the_COVID-19_pandemic#Requested_move_6_June_2020" title="Talk:Misinformation related to the COVID-19 pandemic">discussion</a></li>
<li>23 May 2020 &#8211; <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unity_Church" title="Unity Church">Unity Church</a> <span class="plainlinks"><small>(<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Talk:Unity_Church" title="Talk:Unity Church">talk</a>&#160;·&#160;<a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Unity_Church&amp;action=edit">edit</a>&#160;·&#160;<a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Unity_Church&amp;action=history">hist</a>)</small></span> is requested to be moved to <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Unity_(New_Thought)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Unity (New Thought) (page does not exist)">Unity (New Thought)</a> by <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User:AnandaBliss" title="User:AnandaBliss">AnandaBliss</a> <small>(<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User_talk:AnandaBliss" title="User talk:AnandaBliss">t</a>&#160;·&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:Contributions/AnandaBliss" title="Special:Contributions/AnandaBliss">c</a>)</small>; see <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Talk:Unity_Church#Requested_move_23_May_2020" title="Talk:Unity Church">discussion</a></li>
<li><span style="color:darkred">06 Jun 2020</span> &#8211; <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Laws_against_Holocaust_denial" class="mw-redirect" title="Laws against Holocaust denial">Laws against Holocaust denial</a> <span class="plainlinks"><small>(<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Talk:Laws_against_Holocaust_denial" class="mw-redirect" title="Talk:Laws against Holocaust denial">talk</a>&#160;·&#160;<a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Laws_against_Holocaust_denial&amp;action=edit">edit</a>&#160;·&#160;<a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Laws_against_Holocaust_denial&amp;action=history">hist</a>)</small></span> move request to <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Legality_of_Holocaust_denial" title="Legality of Holocaust denial">Legality of Holocaust denial</a> by <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User:Buidhe" title="User:Buidhe">Buidhe</a> <small>(<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User_talk:Buidhe" title="User talk:Buidhe">t</a>&#160;·&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:Contributions/Buidhe" title="Special:Contributions/Buidhe">c</a>)</small> was <i>moved</i> to <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Legality_of_Holocaust_denial" title="Legality of Holocaust denial">Legality of Holocaust denial</a> <span class="plainlinks"><small>(<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Talk:Legality_of_Holocaust_denial" title="Talk:Legality of Holocaust denial">talk</a>&#160;·&#160;<a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Legality_of_Holocaust_denial&amp;action=edit">edit</a>&#160;·&#160;<a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Legality_of_Holocaust_denial&amp;action=history">hist</a>)</small></span> by <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User:Mdaniels5757" title="User:Mdaniels5757">Mdaniels5757</a> <small>(<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User_talk:Mdaniels5757" title="User talk:Mdaniels5757">t</a>&#160;·