<li><span style="color:darkred">03 Jun 2020</span> &#8211; <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Criticism_of_Holocaust_denial" class="mw-redirect" title="Criticism of Holocaust denial">Criticism of Holocaust denial</a> <span class="plainlinks"><small>(<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Talk:Criticism_of_Holocaust_denial" class="mw-redirect" title="Talk:Criticism of Holocaust denial">talk</a>&#160;·&#160;<a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Criticism_of_Holocaust_denial&amp;action=edit">edit</a>&#160;·&#160;<a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Criticism_of_Holocaust_denial&amp;action=history">hist</a>)</small></span> move request to <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evidence_and_documentation_for_the_Holocaust" title="Evidence and documentation for the Holocaust">Evidence and documentation for the Holocaust</a> by <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User:Buidhe" title="User:Buidhe">Buidhe</a> <small>(<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User_talk:Buidhe" title="User talk:Buidhe">t</a>&#160;·&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:Contributions/Buidhe" title="Special:Contributions/Buidhe">c</a>)</small> was <i>moved</i> to <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evidence_and_documentation_for_the_Holocaust" title="Evidence and documentation for the Holocaust">Evidence and documentation for the Holocaust</a> <span class="plainlinks"><small>(<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Talk:Evidence_and_documentation_for_the_Holocaust" title="Talk:Evidence and documentation for the Holocaust">talk</a>&#160;·&#160;<a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Evidence_and_documentation_for_the_Holocaust&amp;action=edit">edit</a>&#160;·&#160;<a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Evidence_and_documentation_for_the_Holocaust&amp;action=history">hist</a>)</small></span> by <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User:Mdaniels5757" title="User:Mdaniels5757">Mdaniels5757</a> <small>(<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User_talk:Mdaniels5757" title="User talk:Mdaniels5757">t</a>&#160;·&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:Contributions/Mdaniels5757" title="Special:Contributions/Mdaniels5757">c</a>)</small> on 10 Jun 2020; see <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Talk:Criticism_of_Holocaust_denial#Requested_move_3_June_2020" class="mw-redirect" title="Talk:Criticism of Holocaust denial">discussion</a></li>
<li><span style="color:darkred">02 Jun 2020</span> &#8211; <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Murder_of_Seth_Rich" title="Murder of Seth Rich">Murder of Seth Rich</a> <span class="plainlinks"><small>(<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Talk:Murder_of_Seth_Rich" title="Talk:Murder of Seth Rich">talk</a>&#160;·&#160;<a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Murder_of_Seth_Rich&amp;action=edit">edit</a>&#160;·&#160;<a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Murder_of_Seth_Rich&amp;action=history">hist</a>)</small></span> move request to <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Death_of_Seth_Rich" class="mw-redirect" title="Death of Seth Rich">Death of Seth Rich</a> by <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User:Jax_0677" title="User:Jax 0677">Jax 0677</a> <small>(<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User_talk:Jax_0677" title="User talk:Jax 0677">t</a>&#160;·&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:Contributions/Jax_0677" title="Special:Contributions/Jax 0677">c</a>)</small> was <i>not moved</i>; see <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Talk:Murder_of_Seth_Rich#Requested_move_2_June_2020" title="Talk:Murder of Seth Rich">discussion</a></li></ul>
