<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Grover_Furr">Grover Furr</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Wikipedia:Fringe_theories/Noticeboard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3" title="Edit section: Grover Furr">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<p><span id="Grover_Furr"></span><span class="plainlinks nourlexpansion lx"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grover_Furr" title="Grover Furr">Grover Furr</a> (<a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Grover_Furr&amp;action=edit">edit</a>&#160;&#124; <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Talk:Grover_Furr" title="Talk:Grover Furr">talk</a>&#160;&#124; <a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Grover_Furr&amp;action=history">history</a><span class="sysop-show">&#160;&#124; <a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Grover_Furr&amp;action=protect">protect</a>&#160;&#124; <a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Grover_Furr&amp;action=delete">delete</a></span>&#160;&#124; <a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Whatlinkshere/Grover_Furr&amp;limit=999">links</a>&#160;&#124; <a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Grover_Furr&amp;action=watch">watch</a>&#160;&#124; <a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Log&amp;page=Grover+Furr">logs</a>&#160;&#124; <a class="external text" href="http://tools.wmflabs.org/pageviews?pages=Grover_Furr&amp;project=en.wikipedia.org">views</a>)</span>
</p><p>Not a historian, pretends to be one, but is a "revisionist", not a pseudohistorian. --<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User:Hob_Gadling" title="User:Hob Gadling">Hob Gadling</a> (<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User_talk:Hob_Gadling" title="User talk:Hob Gadling">talk</a>) 16:36, 7 May 2020 (UTC)
</p>
<dl><dd>I'm pretty sure he's not actually notable, and <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Articles_for_deletion/Grover_Furr" title="Wikipedia:Articles for deletion/Grover Furr">put this up for AFD</a> a few years ago. What he <i>does</i> have is a huge following amongst his fellow Stalinists. So expect mountains of special pleading and personal attacks - <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User:David_Gerard" title="User:David Gerard">David Gerard</a> (<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User_talk:David_Gerard" title="User talk:David Gerard">talk</a>) 19:08, 7 May 2020 (UTC)</dd>
<dd>Can't stop reading this as Grover Hfuhruhurr . <b><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User:JzG" title="User:JzG">Guy</a></b> <small>(<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User_talk:JzG" title="User talk:JzG">help!</a>)</small> 22:08, 8 May 2020 (UTC)
