<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Abhigya_Anand">Abhigya Anand</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Wikipedia:Fringe_theories/Noticeboard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12" title="Edit section: Abhigya Anand">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<p><span class="plainlinks"> <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Abhigya_Anand&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Abhigya Anand (page does not exist)">Abhigya Anand</a> <span class="plainlinks">(<a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Abhigya_Anand&amp;action=edit">edit</a> | <a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Abhigya_Anand&amp;veaction=edit">visual edit</a> | <a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Abhigya_Anand&amp;action=history">history</a>)</span>&#160;<b>·</b>  <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Talk:Abhigya_Anand&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Talk:Abhigya Anand (page does not exist)"><b>Article talk</b></a> <span class="plainlinks">(<a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Talk:Abhigya_Anand&amp;action=edit">edit</a> | <a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Talk:Abhigya_Anand&amp;action=history">history</a>)</span>&#160;<b>·</b>  <a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Abhigya_Anand&amp;action=watch"><b>Watch</b></a></span> knew it all last year, say sources from this year. I guess this sort of thing happens a lot now. --<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User:Hob_Gadling" title="User:Hob Gadling">Hob Gadling</a> (<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User_talk:Hob_Gadling" title="User talk:Hob Gadling">talk</a>) 13:26, 31 May 2020 (UTC)
</p>
<dl><dd>Sources seem unusually credulous. Claims that someone used psychic powers to predict the current pandemic would fall under <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:EXTRAORDINARY" class="mw-redirect" title="Wikipedia:EXTRAORDINARY">WP:EXTRAORDINARY</a>. - <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User:LuckyLouie" title="User:LuckyLouie">LuckyLouie</a> (<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User_talk:LuckyLouie" title="User talk:LuckyLouie">talk</a>) 15:11, 31 May 2020 (UTC)
